meaningMnemonic: The <radical>feather</radical> radical and <kanji>feather</kanji> are the same in looks as well as in meaning.
readingMnemonic: All these <kanji>feather</kanji>s. You're a birdman or birdwoman, and you're getting ready to fly. But just as you're about to take off, someone dumps <reading>honey</reading> (はね) on you and you're all goopy, unable to go anywhere.
